items.name: Horario-Notifier
items.description: Es una herramienta en Python que sincroniza tu horario personal optimizado con Google Calendar, creando automáticamente eventos con recordatorios en tu teléfono. Perfecto para mantener enfoque, disciplina y productividad a lo largo del día.

items.name: FocusTrackAI
items.description: AI‑Powered Desk Productivity Monitor tracks study activity using YOLOv8 on a laptop webcam. It logs focus, breaks and distractions, sending real‑time alerts to a React parent dashboard with privacy.

items.name: voice-assinstant-python
items.description: “A smart voice-controlled personal assistant built with Python. This assistant can recognize your voice, respond with speech, tell you the time and date, search topics on Wikipedia, play music from YouTube, and even set simple reminders — all hands-free. Perfect for learning speech recognition and building interactive Python applications.”

Notre mission.

items.name: Speed-Limit-Violation-Detection-System
items.description: Speed Limit Violation Detection Streamlit-based computer vision app that detects speeding vehicles from uploaded videos or live webcam feed. The system tracks vehicles using YOLOv8, estimates their speeds, extracts license plate numbers using OCR, and provides a detailed dashboard with downloadable violation data and optional email reporting.
